Hey everyone, stoked to join this workspace.

I'm trying to add the tracking code to my company's React website and I'm a little confused trying to wrap my head around it. Ultimately, I need it for LinkedIn ad tracking as well as incorporating live chat on the site. Here is what I have went with so far:

```import { Helmet } from "react-helmet";

&lt;Helmet&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript" id="hs-script-loader" async defer src="//js.hs-scripts.com/#######.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/Helmet&gt;```
Is this a correct approach for accomplishing what I am trying to do? Any help would be appreciated!
